title: Athena Expects A 'Massive Celebration' From Mercedes Mone If They Win The AEW Women's Tag Titles
summary: Athena wants a 'massive celebration' from Mercedes Mone. On the November 5th edition of AEW Dynamite, Mone and Athena will face off with Willow Nightingale and Harley Cameron in a AEW Women's Tag...
